node.text:
After COVID-Stricken Migrants Seen ‘Coughing, Sneezing’ at a Restaurant. 

HIDALGO COUNTY, Texas (CBSDFW.COM) – The La Joya Police Department issued a public health announcement after an officer approached an undocumented migrant family at Whataburger who told him Border Patrol released them because they had COVID-19.

On July 26 the police department of the small town along the Rio Grande and Mexican border shared details of the incident. They said a concerned citizen at the restaurant waved down the officer. The citizen told him about the family “coughing and sneezing without covering their mouths and not wearing face masks.” Whataburger management also told the officer that they wanted the group to leave as well due to “their disregard to other people’s health.”

They say "We should all be vaccinated!" They want to lock us back down and issue covid passports

node.text:
We know who’s to blame. Joe Biden and QueMala Harris decisions have enabled drug and human traffickers to make fortunes. The income potential from Biden’s willful neglect of our US Border is virtually unlimited as we can see here and who controls the human trafficking. 

Group of “Coyotes” [human traffickers] attack and threaten PNC Police Officers in San Mateo Ixtatán, Huehuetenango, Guatemala. PNC is The Policía Nacional Civil (Guatemala) - The police force of Guatemala

The recording allegedly was done on 7/21/21 and submitted online by a journalist from Guatemala. 

These Police Officers although armed with handguns allow themselves to be beaten and what appears their cell phones are taken from them. 

One of the police officers tries to escape but is chased down by the human smugglers. 

You can tell that there is/was some type of business negotiation happening or already happened between the police officers and the human smugglers, because they ask who put the finger? (Who told on us ~ then mention some type of raid, but it’s hard to understand)

Do not know if the police officers walked away from this as the video ends here. 

Hopefully the @pncdeguatemala PNC Police of Guatemala will look into this if they haven’t already. 

“Se nota que ahí hay negocio entre la PNC y los polleros, porque pregunta quién puso el dedo (se entiende que por una redada) y por eso no se defienden los policías, además se nota que hay un par de mexicanos. Los negocios de la PNC en todo el interior ojalá investiguen!!”

node.title: Group of Human Smugglers threaten and attack Guatemala Police Officers

node.text:
NOW-this week alone- in the Del Rio Sector USBP has apprehended 20K+ illegals in one week alone. 

It's the hottest part of the summer and apprehensions are skyrocketing! 

#USBP Apprehensions surpassed the 1-million milestone in June. These are illegals that have been apprehended and/or turned themselves in to USBP. 

The scary part is, they don’t know how many have gotten away, which could be in the 100,000’s+. They just don’t know.

How irresponsible is this allowing this to happen. Democrats are destroying American before our eyes and we just watch it happen. If Democrats were so concerned about the COVID Delta Variant then why are they allowing illegals to pour in by the THOUSANDS INTO our country non vaccinated with potentially different strands of COVID and who knows what else? 

Especially since we are now seeing thousands from all over the world. Countries that we would have never expected to see at the Mexico border. 

Senile Biden and QueMala Harris are nowhere to be seen. They are MIA.

node.text:
A coronavirus variant known as Lambda, which has largely slid under the radar for the past nine months, is now causing almost all new infections in Peru and it is NOW IN THE UNITED STATES, specifically in Texas and now detected in Louisiana.. 

How did this Variant get into Texas from South America in the first place? Asking for a friend? 

The World Health Organization (WHO) says that the lambda variant—or C.37 variant—has been the COVID-19 carrier in about 81% of infections in Peru since April. The variant was first identified in Peru in August 2020. The WHO declared the lambda variant a variant of interest (VOI) on June 14, a designation that means that it could cause a greater risk than the wild-type variant.

That’s an understatement, according to the investigators at the University of Tokyo, who want the WHO to label the lambda variant a variant of concern (VOC) to put health care systems around the world on notice that this might be their next big challenge.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Latinos With Trump on August 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DRMTா E OF PUBLIC T A LATEST NEWS S from the Texas Department of Public Safety DPS Makes History with Largest Texas Highway Patrol Recruit Graduation'.

node.text:
Texas History — The LARGEST recruit class ever for the Texas Highway Patrol graduated on Friday, according to the Texas Department of Public Safety (DPS). 

The class of 145 new troopers is also one of the most diverse in DPS history, officials said on Facebook. The recruits range in age from 21 to 50 and include 21 women – the most in one recruit class. 

Texas Gov. Greg Abbott spoke at the graduation ceremony. 

“On behalf of the Lone Star State, we are so grateful for your sacrifice and commitment to serving your communities.” 

When you have a Governor who supports its law enforcement officers who wouldn’t want to be a part of an organization like this.

node.text:
BREAKING: Los Angeles County officials have issued an executive order requiring all county employees to get vaccinated against COVID-19. The order will impact more than 110,000 county employees in the largest county in the country. 

Something else that is being worked on for ALL residents of Los Angeles. The Los Angeles City Attorney Mike Feuer sent a letter to county leaders urging them to follow the lead of New York City and require people to show proof of receiving a Vaccine against COVID19 to enter indoor establishments.
